This paper is about image denoising using a convolutional neural network (CNN), which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also focuses on improving the efficiency of the CNN by reducing the number of parameters, which is a common concern in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of gating mechanisms, which are commonly used in multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE).
